title: Nicholas Restaurant - NE Broadway
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Take-out, Catering, Middle Eastern, Lebanese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Lebanese & Middle Eastern cuisine restaurant with a few locations. Lots of the usual meat stuff but also vegan & vegetarian suitable food from hummus and stuffed grape leaves to falafel and vegan lentil soup. Hookah and full bar at this location.
